"&#xa0;\nPatricia A Whelan – Written evidence&#xa0;\n&#xa0;\n&#xa0;\nRef: Upcoming Deregulation Bill, in particular Green Lanes\n&#xa0;\nAll unsealed BOATs and UCRs should be reclassified as RESTRICTED BYWAYS.\n&#xa0;\nI am a member of Yorkshire Dales Local Access Forum and of N.Yorkshire LAF and a member of the British (Horse) Driving Society and am very aware of the problems caused by motorised vehicles – mainly motorcycles on ‘green lanes’.  \n&#xa0;\nI hope that you will consider my submission when assembling forthcoming Deregulation Bill.\n&#xa0;\nThank you for your attention.\n&#xa0;\n&#xa0;\n&#xa0;\n31 August 2013\n&#xa0;\n"